## n8n@0.194.0 View the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.193.5...n8n@0.194.0) for this version.
**Release date:** 2022-09-15 This release includes new nodes: a Gmail trigger, Google Cloud Storage, and Adalo. It also contains major overhauls of the Gmail and Merge nodes.
